::Grimlock::
   
  The workers at the shuttle port attempted to stop Grimlock from taking a shuttle. They wanted written approval from Lord Perseus. Big mistake. They wer not seriously harmed but they all now know not to get in the way of a Dinobot.
   
  The bay doors are blasted apart as Grimlock pilots the shuttle away from Atlantis. Grimlock directs the shuttle towards Olympus where he will carry out the orders of Jotunn: Find Motherload and tell her we need Stormblaze.
   
  ::Jhiaxus-Hevn::
   
  The Hevn puppet watches as the shuttle blasts it's way out of the bay and heads into the sky. Through the puppet Jhiaxus is wondering how things are run in this city. He knows that he must stay low-ki and wait for the chance to snatch Nightlight.
